          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "review_2": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "post_author": "Jennifer K.",
            "post_author_verified": true,
            "post_time": "1 month ago",
            "post_text": "<p>As someone who's tried every eye cream under the sun, I was hesitant to try a device. But WOW. The fine lines around my eyes have visibly reduced after just 4 weeks of daily use. My friends keep asking what I'm doing differently. This is my secret weapon! 💕</p>",
            "post_reactions": "203",
            "post_reactions_text": "❤️ 203",
            "post_comments_text": "31 Comments"
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "review_3": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "post_author": "Michelle T.",
            "post_author_verified": true,
            "post_time": "3 weeks ago",
            "post_text": "<p>I'm a nurse and I've seen red light therapy used clinically. Having this technology at home is a game changer. My patients always ask about my skin and I tell them about RevitalEyes. The results speak for themselves. FDA cleared gives me confidence.</p>",
            "post_reactions": "312",
            "post_reactions_text": "❤️ 312",
            "post_comments_text": "47 Comments"
