        "faq_2": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is it safe to use around the eyes?",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes! RevitalEyes is FDA cleared and specifically designed for the delicate under-eye area. The wavelengths used (660nm and 590nm) are completely safe for use near the eyes. Always keep the device at least 1cm from your eyelids and do not look directly into the light.</p>"
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_3": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How often should I use RevitalEyes?",
            "row_content": "<p>We recommend using RevitalEyes once daily for 10 minutes per eye. Consistency is key — make it part of your morning skincare routine for the best results. You can safely use it up to twice daily if desired.</p>"
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_4": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
