            "heading": "What does your return policy cover?",
            "row_content": "<p>We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee. If you're not completely satisfied with your results, simply return the device in its original packaging for a full refund — no questions asked. We're that confident in RevitalEyes.</p>"
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_5": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use it with my eye cream?",
            "row_content": "<p>Absolutely! We actually recommend applying your favorite eye cream immediately after your RevitalEyes session. Light therapy has been shown to increase the absorption of topical skincare products by up to 40%, making your eye cream even more effective.</p>"
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_6": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How do I charge RevitalEyes?",
            "row_content": "<p>RevitalEyes charges via USB-C (cable included). A full charge takes approximately 1.5 hours and provides up to 30 days of daily use. An LED indicator will show you the battery status at all times.</p>"
